4. Ask One Ally

You only need one person to say yes.

    Hey, Im trying to stay grounded and move forward today, but Im in a rough spot. If you can cashapp/venmo $10-20 so I can eat and cool down, Id really appreciate it.

5. Return for Cash or Gift Card

If you have:

  • Old receipts
  • Items from Walmart, Target, etc.
